sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Tx as Primary Worker (CDC trigger)
    participant Led as SyncOpLedger
    participant Out as BackupOutbox (envelope builder)
    participant Pri as Primary Worker (sender)
    participant BE1 as Backup Node BE-1
    participant App as Apply Pipeline (22-…md)
    participant DB as Backup App-DB

    Tx->>Led: INSERT SyncOp (SyncOpSeq monotonic)
    Out->>Led: SELECT WHERE SyncOpSeq > Watermark
    Out->>Out: Build envelope (FromSeq..ToSeq), seal under Active KeyEpoch
    Pri->>BE1: POST /API/V1/Backup/IncrementalDiff (S2S OAuth, PairingId)
    BE1->>App: Hand off sealed envelope
    App->>App: Stage 1 Decrypt → 2 Open → 3 Validate (V1–V7)
    alt Idempotent replay (V7 hit)
        App-->>BE1: 200 OK (LastAcceptedSyncOpSeq unchanged)
    else New envelope
        App->>DB: BEGIN IMMEDIATE
        App->>DB: Dispatch upserts/deletes per row
        App->>DB: UPDATE BackupSyncWatermark = ToSeq
        App->>DB: COMMIT
        App-->>BE1: 200 OK { LastAcceptedSyncOpSeq: ToSeq }
    end
    BE1-->>Pri: ACK
    Pri->>Pri: Advance local cursor and mark envelope Acked

    Note over App,DB: Any Stage failure → BackupApplyDeadLetter (no silent skip per CODE RED).
